#11201
Knight's Mansion, Entryway~
You are in the entry room of the Knight's mansion.  Looking around here you
find it to be very extravegant.  It has a wood theme to the building, and
furniture, all of which is furnished and polished to perfection in sight.
You see some broken glass on the floor near your feet, which probably came
from a matching broken window above the mess, sloppily left there.  In the
middle of the mess is a rock, probably thrown in by one of those hilarious
rogues, though you doubt the knight will be very happy when he finds out...
~
