Knight's Mansion~
You look around at the nice wooden walls and relating furniture.  It is a nice,
polished dark brown, and some things have a red to them, like the velvety
lining on the back of a chair.  You try to estimate how much this place must
have cost, obviously a fortune: your tax dollars at work.  You see above you
the continuation of a winding staircase which comes from the room to the north.
