#11203
Knight's Mansion~
You see the staircase above descending ever closer to the ground as it wraps
around the middle area of the building, between the four rooms, an interesting
vision of architecture no doubt.  You look around the room at paintings upon
the walls.  There are also shelves of books upon the north, west, and southern
walls, and a comfotable looking chair beside a small table in the center.  On
the wall is a fireplace.  There is no lit fire in it currently, it holds only
some cinder and ash.  It is rather big, somebody could probably fit in it if
they had a reason to.
~
