Knight's Mansion, First Floor~
You now find yourself at the base of the winding staircase, leading up to a
second floor.  Besides that, there are a number of statues here, most likely
dummies of some sort, set upon stands, and suited in fine armors.  You look
upon the ever shiny gleam of the armor, the helmets, gauntlets, etc, and the
fierce looking spiked end of a mace in one hand or the razor sharp edge of a
double edged sword in another.
